<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mental Clinic - Landing Page</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset default styles */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    /* Header */
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px 50px;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    header .logo {
      font-size: 1.8em;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    nav a {
      margin: 0 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #dcd6ff;
    }

    .header-buttons a {
      margin-left: 15px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 2px solid white;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .header-buttons a.login {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: white;
    }

    .header-buttons a.register {
      background-color: white;
      color: #4f46e5;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .header-buttons a:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      background: url('https://berkeleyclinic.ie/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/AdobeStock_484962569-min-scaled.jpeg') no-repeat center center/cover;
      height: 90vh;
      color: white;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      max-width: 600px;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }

    .hero button {
      padding: 12px 30px;
      font-size: 1em;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #4f46e5;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
    }

    .hero button:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Sections */
    section {
      padding: 80px 50px;
    }

    section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.2em;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      color: #4f46e5;
    }

    section p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* Pricing Cards */
    .pricing-cards {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .card {
      background-color: #f9f9ff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 30px;
      width: 250px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #4f46e5;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 1em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .card button {
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border: none;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: opacity 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }

    .card button:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .pricing-cards {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      nav {
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <div class="logo">Nafsi Clinic System</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#home">Home</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact Us</a>
      <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="header-buttons">
      <a href="/login" class="login">Login</a>
      <a href="/register" class="register">Register</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero" id="home">
   <h1>Smart Clinic Management for Mental Health Professionals</h1>
<p>
  Simplify your workflow. With Nafsi Clinic System, therapists and secretaries can 
  manage appointments, digitize medical records, issue prescriptions, and keep patients 
  on track with automated notifications and medication reminders — all in one secure platform.
</p>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
<p>
  Nafsi Clinic System is built for mental health clinics and professionals who want to 
  focus on patient care instead of paperwork. Our platform makes it easy to schedule and 
  manage appointments, send reminders, digitize records and prescriptions, and support patients 
  between sessions with automated medication notifications. Secure, private, and accessible 
  anywhere — we bring modern clinic management to your practice.
</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Section -->
  <section id="pricing">
    <h2>Pricing Plans</h2>
    <div class="pricing-cards">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Demo</h3>
    <p>
      - 1 Therapist, 1 Patient, 1 Secretary <br>
      - Appointment scheduling <br>
      - Basic record-keeping <br>
      - Limited data access (3 per day)
    </p>
    <button>Select</button>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Standard</h3>
    <p>
      - 1 therapist <br>
      - 10 patients <br>
      - Full appointment & notification system <br>
      - Digital records & prescriptions <br>
      - Patient medication reminders
    </p>
    <button>Select</button>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Premium</h3>
    <p>
      - Everything in Standard <br>
      - Advanced analytics & reporting <br>
      - Priority support <br>
      - Custom clinic branding <br>
      - Unlimited patients & data access
    </p>
    <button>Select</button>
  </div>
</div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Have questions or need assistance? Reach out to our team via email at support@mindcareclinic.com or call us at (123) 456-7890. We are here to help you every step of the way.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 MindCare Clinic. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
